        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Expand Medicaid Now Act</b></p> <p>This bill temporarily increases the Federal Medical Assistance Percentage (i.e., federal matching rate) for states that elect to participate in Medicaid expansion (pursuant to the Patient Protection and Affordable Care Act) if they have not already done so.</p>]]>
        </text>
